OL,3,CBattle of Flowers finances show
OL,4,C10,000% increase in spending on
OL,5,Centertainment
OL,7,FJersey's last Battle of Flowers made a
OL,8,Fmore than #350,000 loss, according to
OL,9,Ftheir financial records.
OL,11,FITV Channel News has been sent a copy
OL,12,Fof last year's accounts, detailing how
OL,13,Fmoney was spent in 2023 and 2024.
OL,15,FRecords found more than #153,700 was
OL,16,Fspent on entertainment such as
OL,17,Fheadline act Sam Ryder - a 10,000%
OL,18,Fincrease compared to just under #1,500
OL,19,Fspent in 2023.
