OL,7,FThis is shown as 'little gigs' on the
OL,8,Fexpense report.
OL,10,FFinancial accounts also show that the
OL,11,Fevent made a net deficit in the past
OL,12,Ftwo years, with almost #745,000 spent
OL,13,Foverall in 2024.
OL,15,FIt comes after the strategy group set
OL,16,Fup to save the event said that
OL,17,Ffinancial and leadership issues proved
OL,18,F"insurmountable".
