OL,7,FThe group said extensive efforts -
OL,8,Fincluding "intensive discussions with
OL,9,Fgovernment ministers and officials" -
OL,10,Ffailed to secure Battle's future.
OL,12,FMany exhibitors also claim they have
OL,13,Fstill not been paid for 2024, with
OL,14,Fconcerns over how they will recoup
OL,15,Ftheir cash.
